## Execution Protocol

1. Select the target Design Doc.
2. If requested, generate test skeletons with `dev-workflows-blazor:acceptance-test-generator`.
3. Invoke `dev-workflows-blazor:work-planner` with the Design Doc and any generated test skeleton paths.
4. Present the resulting work plan for approval and revise if needed.
